Package jcomb.core

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InstanceDependent
    An instance dependent object has to be reinitialized for each test class instance.
    JCombContext
    Holds information for the current combinatorial test of a test method.
    TestInputGenerator
    A TestInputGenerator is used for generating all relevant input combinations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InputCombination
    This class represents a combination of parameter values used as an input for one test method call.
    JCombCore
    A factory class to create TestInputGenerators based on the supplied information.
    PartialJCombContext
    This class can be used if for a given test method not the whole JCombContext of the test class should be used.
    SingleParameterInputGenerator
    A basic TestInputGenerator used if only 1 parameter is supplied.
    StandardJCombContext
    The default implementation of an JCombContext.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Algorithm
    An enum for all the possible algorithms supported by jcomb.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    JCombException
    A general exception class, that is used if some problem is found with the current test setup.
